-- Gold Declines 0.4% to $1,314.47 an Ounce After Rising to Record on Oct. 1
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   L a r k i n
-- 2010-10-04T09:55:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/gold-declines-0-4-to-1-314-47-an-ounce-after-rising-to-record-on-oct-1.html
Gold for immediate delivery declined
0.4 percent to $1,314.47 an ounce at 10:54 a.m. in London. The
metal reached a record $1,320.70 on Oct. 1.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nicholas Larkin at 
 nlarkin1@bloomberg.net  